  "instructions": [
    "Heat a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the unsalted butter and let it melt.",
    "Add the diced chicken breast and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the cumin, chili powder, and salt, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the nuka-pickle and stir to combine.",
    "Warm the corn tortillas by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "Assemble the tacos by placing a spoonful of the chicken mixture onto a tortilla and topping with shredded cheese, chopped cilantro, and a dollop of sour cream.",
    "Serve immediately and garnish with orange zest and a squeeze of lime juice.",
    "Ensure poultry is cooked to an internal temperature of 74°C / 165°F (juices run clear, no pink remaining) before serving."
